languages.text: "Вы, мон-кай, одинаково жутки в своем самоотречении, какой бы путь ни избрали".
"You mon-keigh are all equally unsettling in your self-renunciations, regardless of what path you might choose."

languages.text: "Ihr Chem-Pan-Sey seid alle gleichermaßen verstörend in Eurer Selbstverleugnung, welchen Pfad Ihr auch wählt."

languages.text: « Vous autres mon-keigh ne cessez de me surprendre par votre capacité à vous sacrifier pour une cause, quelle que soit la voie que vous ayez choisie. »
languages.original_text: "You mon-keigh are all equally unsettling in your self-renunciations, regardless of what path you might choose."

languages.text: «Los mon-keigh sois perturbadores en vuestra renuncia a vosotros mismos, sea cual sea la senda elegida».
languages.original_text: "You mon-keigh are all equally unsettling in your self-renunciations, regardless of what path you might choose."

languages.text: 「お前たちモン＝ケイは、その自己放棄において、皆等しく不安よ。どんな道を選ぼうとも」
languages.original_text: "You mon-keigh are all equally unsettling in your self-renunciations, regardless of what path you might choose."

traits.locale_text: 「お前たちモン＝ケイは、その自己放棄において、皆等しく不安よ。どんな道を選ぼうとも」

languages.text: “无论你们这些猴子选择了什么样的道路，你们自我弃绝的那股劲头，都一样令人不安。”
